\c 22
\s UMikhaya ukhuluma ngokunqotshwa kukaAhabi loJehoshafathi
\p
\v 1 Bahlala-ke iminyaka emithathu kungekho impi phakathi kweSiriya loIsrayeli.
\v 2 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wesithathu\x + 2 Lan. 18.2-34.\x* uJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda\x + 15.24. 22.41.\x* wehlela enkosini yakoIsrayeli\x + 20.7.\x*.
\v 3 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi encekwini zayo: Liyazi yini ukuthi iRamothi-Gileyadi ingeyethu\x + 4.13. Josh. 21.38. 2 Kho. 8.28. 9.1,14. 2 Lan. 22.5. Dute. 4.43. Josh. 20.8. 1 Lan. 6.80.\x*? Kodwa sithule, singayithathi esandleni senkosi yeSiriya.
\v 4 Yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: Uzahamba lami empini eRamothi-Gileyadi yini? UJehoshafathi wasesithi enkosini yakoIsrayeli: Nginjengawe, njengabantu bami banjalo abantu bakho, njengamabhiza ami anjalo amabhiza akho\x + 2 Kho. 3.7.\x*.
\v 5 UJehoshafathi wasesithi enkosini yakoIsrayeli: Akubuze lamuhla ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 6 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasibuthanisa abaprofethi abangaba ngamadoda angamakhulu amane, yathi kubo: Ngihambe yini ukuyamelana leRamothi-Gileyadi empini kumbe ngiyekele? Basebesithi: Yenyuka, ngoba iNkosi izayinikela esandleni senkosi\x + 18.19.\x*.
\v 7 UJehoshafathi wasesithi: Kakusekho yini lapha umprofethi weN\nd kosi\nd* esingambuza\x + 2 Kho. 3.11.\x*?
\v 8 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: Kusekhona indoda eyodwa, uMikhaya indodana kaImla, e\add si\add*ngabuza ngaye eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kodwa mina ngiyamzonda, ngoba kaprofethi okuhle ngami, kodwa okubi. UJehoshafathi wasesithi: Inkosi ingatsho njalo.
\v 9 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasibiza induna yathi: Landa masinyane uMikhaya indodana kaImla.
\v 10 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli loJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda babehlezi, ngulowo lalowo esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi, begqoke izembatho \add zabo\add*, besebaleni lokubhulela ekungeneni kwesango leSamariya\x + 16.24.\x*, njalo bonke abaprofethi babeprofetha phambi kwabo.
\v 11 UZedekhiya indodana kaKhenahana wasezenzela izimpondo zensimbi\x + Zek. 1.18,19. Jer. 27.2. 28.10. Seb. 21.11.\x*, wathi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngalezi uzahlaba amaSiriya uze uwaqede\x + Dute. 33.17.\x*.
\v 12 Labo bonke abaprofethi baprofetha njalo, besithi: Yenyukela eRamothi-Gileyadi, uphumelele; ngoba uJehova uzayinikela esandleni senkosi.
\p
\v 13 Isithunywa esasiyebiza uMikhaya sakhuluma laye sathi: Khangela-ke, amazwi abaprofethi ngamlomo munye mahle enkosini; ake ilizwi lakho lifanane lelizwi lomunye wabo, ukhulume okuhle.
\v 14 Kodwa uMikhaya wathi: Kuphila kukaJehova\x + 17.1.\x*, lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekutshoyo kimi lokho ngizakukhuluma\x + Nani 22.18.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Esefikile enkosini, inkosi yathi kuye: Mikhaya, siye eRamothi-Gileyadi empini kumbe siyekele? Wasesithi kuyo: Yenyuka, uphumelele; ngoba uJehova uzayinikela esandleni senkosi.
\v 16 Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Ngizakufungisa kuze kube kangaki ukuthi ungangitsheli lutho ngaphandle kweqiniso ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*?
\v 17 Wasesithi: Ngabona uIsrayeli wonke ehlakazekile phezu kwezintaba njengezimvu ezingelamelusi; uJehova wathi: Laba kabalankosi, kababuyele, ngulowo lalowo endlini yakhe ngokuthula\x + Nani 27.17.\x*.
\v 18 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: Kangikutshelanga yini ukuthi kayikuprofetha okuhle ngami kodwa okubi\x + 22.8.\x*?
\v 19 Wasesithi: Ngakho zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngibone iN\nd kosi\nd* ihlezi esihlalweni sayo sobukhosi\x + Isa. 6.1. Hez. 1.26. 10.1. Dan. 7.9. Isam. 4.2. 20.4.\x*, lamabutho wonke amazulu emi phansi kwayo ngakwesokunene sayo langakwesokhohlo sayo\x + Jobe 1.6. 2.1. Hlab. 103.20,21. Zek. 1.10. Mat. 18.10. Heb. 1.7,14. 12.22. Isam. 9.16. Dute. 33.2.\x*.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Ngubani ozahuga uAhabi ukuthi enyuke ayewela eRamothi-Gileyadi? Omunye-ke watsho njalo, lomunye watsho njalo.
\v 21 Kwasekuphuma umoya, wema phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: Mina ngizamhuga.
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Ngani? Wasesithi: Ngizaphuma ngibe ngumoya wamanga emlonyeni wabo bonke abaprofethi bakhe\x + Hlu. 9.23. Isa. 19.14. Jer. 4.10. Hez. 14.9. 2 Thes. 2.11.\x*. Yasisithi: Uza\add m\add*huga, njalo uzaphumelela; phuma wenze njalo.
\v 23 Ngakho-ke, khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* ifake umoya wamanga emlonyeni walababaprofethi bakho bonke, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulume okubi ngawe.
\v 24 UZedekhiya indodana kaKhenahana wasesondela, watshaya uMikhaya esihlathini\x + Lilo 3.30. Mika 5.1. Mat. 5.39. 26.67. Mark. 14.65. Joha. 18.22. Seb. 23.2.\x*, wathi: UMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wedlula ngani esuka kimi ukuyakhuluma lawe?
\v 25 UMikhaya wasesithi: Khangela, uzakubona mhlalokho lapho uzangena ekamelweni elingaphakathi ukuyacatsha.
\v 26 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi: Thatha uMikhaya, mbuyisele kuAmoni umbusi womuzi lakuJowashi indodana yenkosi,
\v 27 uthi: Itsho njalo inkosi: Fakani lo entolongweni, limdlise isinkwa sohlupho lamanzi ohlupho\x + 2 Lan. 16.10.\x* ngize ngibuye ngokuthula.
\v 28 UMikhaya wasesithi: Uba uphenduka isibili ngokuthula\x + Hlu. 8.9.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* kayikhulumanga ngami. Wasesithi: Zwanini, bantu, lina lonke\x + Nani 16.29. Dute. 18.20-22.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli loJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda basebesenyukela eRamothi-Gileyadi.
\v 30 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: \add Ngi\add*zazifihla isimo, \add ngi\add*ngene empini, kodwa wena gqoka izembatho zakho\x + 1 Sam. 28.8.\x*. Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasizifihla isimo, yangena empini\x + 1 Sam. 28.8.\x*.
\v 31 Inkosi yeSiriya yayilaye induna zezinqola ezingamatshumi amathathu lambili ayelazo\x + 20.1,24.\x*, esithi: Lingalwi lomncinyane loba lomkhulu, kodwa lenkosi yakoIsrayeli kuphela\x + 20.33,34.\x*.
\v 32 Kwasekusithi induna zezinqola zibona uJehoshafathi zona zathi: Isibili yiyo inkosi yakoIsrayeli. Zaseziphambuka ukulwa zimelene layo\x + 2 Lan. 18.31.\x*; uJehoshafathi waseklabalala\x + 2 Lan. 18.31.\x*.
\v 33 Kwasekusithi induna zezinqola zibona ukuthi kwakungeyisiyo inkosi yakoIsrayeli, zaphenduka ekuyilandeleni.
\v 34 Umuntu \add othile\add* wasedonsa idandili lakhe engananzeleli, wahlaba inkosi yakoIsrayeli phakathi kwenhlangano lebhatshi lensimbi; yasisithi kumtshayeli wenqola yayo: Phendula isandla sakho, ungikhuphe phakathi kwebutho, ngoba ngilimele kakhulu.
\v 35 Impi yasikhula mhlalokho; njalo inkosi yayisekelwe enqoleni yayo iqondene lamaSiriya, yafa ntambama; igazi lenxeba lagelezela ngaphansi kwenqola.
\v 36 Ekutshoneni kwelanga kwadabula isimemezelo ebuthweni sisithi: Wonke \add ka\add*ye emzini wakibo, laye wonke elizweni lakibo.
\p
\v 37 Ngakho inkosi yafa, yalethwa eSamariya; basebeyingcwaba inkosi eSamariya.
\v 38 \add Omunye\add* wasegezisa inqola echibini leSamariya, lezinja zakhotha igazi layo, lapho amawule ayegeza khona, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhulumayo\x + 20.42. 21.19.\x*.
\p
\v 39 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAhabi, lakho konke akwenzayo, lendlu yempondo zendlovu ayakhayo\x + Amos 3.15.\x*, lemizi yonke ayakhayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\v 40 UAhabi waselala laboyise. UAhaziya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\s Ukubusa kukaJehoshafathi
\p
\v 41 UJehoshafathi indodana kaAsa waba-ke yinkosi phezu kukaJuda ngomnyaka wesine kaAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli.
\v 42 Njalo uJehoshafathi wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lanhlanu lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa eJerusalema iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanhlanu. Lebizo likanina lalinguAzuba indodakazi kaShilehi\x + 2 Lan. 20.31-33.\x*.
\v 43 Njalo wahamba ngayo yonke indlela kaAsa uyise\x + 2 Lan. 17.3,6.\x*, kaphambukanga kuyo, ukwenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*. Loba kunjalo indawo eziphakemeyo kazisuswanga; abantu babelokhu benikela imihlatshelo, betshisa impepha endaweni eziphakemeyo\x + 15.14.\x*.
\v 44 UJehoshafathi wasesenza ukuthula lenkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Lan. 18.1. 19.2.\x*.
\p
\v 45 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehoshafathi, lobuqhawe abenzayo, lokuthi walwa njani, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 20.34.\x*?
\v 46 Lensali yezinkotshana ezazisele ensukwini zikaAsa uyise wayikhupha elizweni\x + 15.12. Dute. 23.17.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Njalo eEdoma kwakungelankosi\x + 2 Sam. 8.14. 2 Kho. 3.9.\x*, umbambeli wayeyinkosi\x + 4.5.\x*.
\v 48 UJehoshafathi\x + 2 Lan. 20.35-37.\x* wenza imikhumbi yeThashishi\x + 10.22.\x* ukuya eOfiri uku\add landa\add* igolide\x + 9.28.\x*; kodwa kayiyanga, ngoba imikhumbi yephukela eEziyoni-Geberi\x + Nani 33.35.\x*.
\v 49 Ngalesosikhathi uAhaziya indodana kaAhabi wathi kuJehoshafathi: Inceku zami kazihambe lenceku zakho emikhunjini. Kodwa uJehoshafathi kafunanga.
\p
\v 50 UJehoshafathi waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa kuboyise emzini kaDavida uyise. UJoramu indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Lan. 21.1.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaAhaziya koIsrayeli
\p
\v 51 UAhaziya indodana kaAhabi waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli eSamariya ngomnyaka wetshumi lesikhombisa kaJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda; wabusa phezu kukaIsrayeli iminyaka emibili\x + 22.40,49.\x*.
\v 52 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, wahamba ngendlela kayise, langendlela kanina, langendlela kaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati\x + 16.30,31.\x* owenza uIsrayeli one\x + 14.16.\x*.
\v 53 Wasekhonza uBhali, wakhothamela kuye, wayithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, njengakho konke ayekwenzile uyise\x + 16.30,31.\x*.